{"tid":837172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英以劫機喻港獨主張","createTime":"2018-09-26T07:28:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T10:41:33.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c7a4d5dc75c4a67e28c402e82612924563d0de1d","tid":837172,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T07:28:24.000Z","msg":"政府於日前刊憲禁止香港民族黨運作，全國政協副主席、前行政長官梁振英在Facebook發文，以劫機比喻港獨的主張。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英引述報道指公民黨黨魁楊岳橋提及，非常質疑保安局禁止民族黨運作的理據是否充分，民族黨到現時為止，只停留在一個「講」字，似乎沒有構成公共安全的危險，梁振英以「飛機乘客可以在飛機上主張劫機嗎？」作為反駁。<br />\n<br />\n對於楊岳橋表示「參選本身是憲法賦予的權利」，梁振英反駁指「違反《基本法》可以參選嗎？」，最後更反問楊岳橋是否反對港獨。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1952988/%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B1%E4%BB%A5%E5%8A%AB%E6%A9%9F%E5%96%BB%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8%E4%B8%BB%E5%BC%B5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F1952988%2F%25E6%25A2%2581%25E6%258C%25AF%25E8%258B%25B1%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E5%258A%25AB%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%2596%25BB%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258D%25A8%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25BC%25B5&d=kfSNCAAQUomQqF8ClgZlJk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=ae0f202c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1952988/%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B1%E4%BB%A5%E5%8A%AB%E6%A9%9F%E5%96%BB%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8%E4%B8%BB%E5%BC%B5</a>"},{"pid":"2a9094d142eb5d4eb4270ab2f0150998fc1f3806","tid":837172,"uid":49457,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T07:30:58.000Z","msg":"架飛機咪一早比689班人劫撚左囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86f3c973ed27b340f10aa147bf4be732cc20ce57","tid":837172,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T07:32:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/SopI3R3AGuQrjnoElY1Jyg--~B/aD00MDA7dz01MDA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20180726a112550.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fap